                        model="text-container-text"
                        modelFields="[text@richtext]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>We are constantly striving to raise the bar in our workplace and in the communities where we work and live.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;strong>Building a world-class workforce&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xa; &lt;li>Through inclusive education programs, we give colleagues around the world the opportunity to learn from one another while we build high performing teams.&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>We prioritize leadership development and provide one-on-one mentoring that pairs high performing talent with AbbVie senior executives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;strong>&lt;br>Driving an inclusive culture through awareness and understanding&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xa; &lt;li>We believe that having a voice is about more than volume – it is about belonging – feeling empowered to share your unique perspective as part of a collaborative, high-performing team.&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbvie.com/join-us/life-at-abbvie/employee-resource-groups.html&quot;>employee resource groups&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;are open to all employees and reflect our belief that inclusion benefits everyone and drives high performance.&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>We are committed to accessibility for all – so our employees can reach their full potential.&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;br>&lt;strong>Creating connections and fostering well-being&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xa; &lt;li>We partner with employees on their well-being journey, connecting them to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbvie.com/join-us/life-at-abbvie/well-being-in-the-workplace.html&quot;>tools and support&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;at work and at home.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>We’ve made dialogue an everyday way of life at AbbVie, fostering connection to one another and creating space for all to contribute their unique value.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>As part of AbbVie’s commitment to building community, our Employee Resource Groups (ERGs) partner with the AbbVie Foundation to support a variety of nonprofit organizations.&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>"/>
                </text_container>
